data.title: Geheimnisse der Gerichtsmedizin" Mistaken for Dead (TV Episode 2001)
data.meta_description: Mistaken for Dead: With Peter Thomas, Richard Boggs, Ellis Greene, John Hawkins. California, 1988: Dr. Richard Boggs, John Hawkins and Melvin Eugene Hanson attempt insurance fraud. They would have gotten away with it, and tried again, if Dr. Boggs hadn't made several mistakes.
